<html>
  <head>
    <title>{{projectName}}</title>
    <style>
      body { font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; word-wrap: break-word; }
    </style>
  </head>
  <body>
    <p>
      Contest <a href="{{contestUrl}}">{{contestName}}</a> has been finished and is pending review by the admin team.
      {{#if isUnofficialCompetition}}
        <strong>Please provide at least two photos of the competition setup</strong> (i.e. scrambling area, competition area, etc.) in response to this email.
      {{/if}}
    </p>

    <p>If you find an error in the results that needs to be corrected, please let the admin team know in a reply to this email. <strong>Make sure to use "Reply All"!</strong></p>

    {{#if organizationName}}
      <p><strong>Please donate to support the development of RecordRanks - the software that powers {{organizationName}}.</strong></p>
    {{/if}}

    <a href="{{rrDonationLink}}">Support the project</a>
    
    <p>@Admin team: Review the results and publish them so they become included in the rankings.</p>
  </body>
</html>